1. Prerequesites

To build FileZilla Server you'll need the following:

- Visual Studio 2013 Professional
- OpenSSL
- Zlib

Note: Express editions of Visual Studio won't do the trick as FileZilla Server depends on MFC.

2. Preparation

- Compile Zlib and OpenSSL, see their respective documentation for instructions
- Copy source\Dependencies.props.example to source\Dependencies.props
- Open source\Dependencies.props in a text editor and change the 5 paths in it

3. Building FileZilla

- Open "source\FileZilla Server.sln" in Visual Studio and hit F5.